cfedfa2ccfd681b83a830193f28b.webm?t=1726413541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801860/extras/a491cfedfa2ccfd681b83a830193f28b.mp4?t=1726413541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>-Move quickly throughout the store, dodging enemy fire and ambushing your attackers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801860/extras/f42bc5c1938afdbd50d6172b9b2910c3.poster.avif?t=1726413541\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801860/extras/f42bc5c1938afdbd50d6172b9b2910c3.webm?t=1726413541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801860/extras/f42bc5c1938afdbd50d6172b9b2910c3.mp4?t=1726413541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>-Quickly chain attacks together for ultimate carnage, score 50 kills to survive the night.",
